---
// ObiSection — WP-05 scaffold stub, WP-09 fills in.
//
// Reserved layout for the company-proof / lore closing beat: the "Welcome to
// your Obi" story (18-months-running-our-company narrative, per-claim
// sourcing per WP-09's DoD), the closing CTA pair, and the Obi/ozi gloss.
// All of that content lives in the CURRENT src/pages/index.astro's closing
// CTA section today and is copy-accounted in WP-05's report as "moved to
// WP-09 scope" — nothing here is invented, this section only reserves the
// seam WP-09 builds into.
//
// Tone: dark — the narrative returns to the theatre pole for the closing
// beat before the light subscribe section underneath it (per D-01 seam plan).
---

<section class="sk-section" id="obi">
	<div class="sk-wrap">
		<!-- WP-09 -->
		<div class="stub-box" aria-hidden="true">
			<p class="stub-box__label">Obi / lore / company-proof — reserved for WP-09</p>
			<p class="stub-box__note">
				The "Welcome to your Obi" story, closing CTA, and proof/gloss lines
				land here (moved from the current production index.astro's closing
				CTA section; WP-09 re-sources every claim).
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.stub-box {
		border: 1px dashed var(--site-border-strong);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg, 10px);
		padding: var(--space-8, 32px) var(--space-6, 24px);
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--site-faint);
	}
	.stub-box__label {
		font-family: var(--site-font-mono);
		letter-spacing: 0.14em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-2, 8px);
	}
	.stub-box__note {
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 46ch;
		margin-inline: auto;
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
	}
</style>
